{"tid":402344,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"Microsoft 將推出 Windows Defender 收費版","createTime":"2017-09-16T11:08:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-16T11:09:34.000Z","uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2a4d21f5354d7556f49c25a93dcfbf91ae9b50df","tid":402344,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T11:08:15.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">Windows 收費版防毒出爐 內置進階防護效能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/1900008/Windows%20%E6%94%B6%E8%B2%BB%E7%89%88%E9%98%B2%E6%AF%92%E5%87%BA%E7%88%90%20%E9%80%B2%E9%9A%8E%E9%98%B2%E8%AD%B7%E6%95%88%E8%83%BD\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F1900008%2FWindows%2520%25E6%2594%25B6%25E8%25B2%25BB%25E7%2589%2588%25E9%2598%25B2%25E6%25AF%2592%25E5%2587%25BA%25E7%2588%2590%2520%25E9%2580%25B2%25E9%259A%258E%25E9%2598%25B2%25E8%25AD%25B7%25E6%2595%2588%25E8%2583%25BD&d=Xlf0lsyH9VACQRQFIBnRs57TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=f40a80b2\" target=\"_blank\">https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/1900008/Windows%20%E6%94%B6%E8%B2%BB%E7%89%88%E9%98%B2%E6%AF%92%E5%87%BA%E7%88%90%20%E9%80%B2%E9%9A%8E%E9%98%B2%E8%AD%B7%E6%95%88%E8%83%BD</a></div><br />\n<br />\n無論是 Win10 內置的 Windows Defender，又或者市面上的各類免費防毒軟件，包括最新推出的 Kaspersky 免費版，一般用戶都有大量防毒選擇。不過，今日(9月8日)微軟推出收費版 Windows Defender Advanced Threat Protection (ATP)公測，究竟做乜撚嘢事？<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/1900000/1900008/996web7201_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1900000%2F1900008%2F996web7201_1024.jpg&h=88ae9c79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</div><br />\nWindows Defender Advanced Threat Protection (ATP) 將會結合 Windows Defender、防火牆、SmartScreen 等基本功能，還會提供裝置管理及漏洞防護等進階功能，面向的主要是企業客戶。之不過，向來微軟的各款保安工具，在各大病毒測試中均表現平平，究竟有多少人願意投下信任一票是很大的問號。目前 ATP 已展開公測，設有 90 天免費試用，有性趣的巴打可以去做白老鼠試伏。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/windowsforbusiness/windows-atp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.microsoft.com%2Fen-us%2Fwindowsforbusiness%2Fwindows-atp&d=Xlf0lsyH9VACQRQFIBnRs57TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=8f8f6235\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/windowsforbusiness/windows-atp</a><br />\n<br />\n點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </div>"},{"pid":"ddc88a244f9efd650e20a7e73967aaabe2ebfce0","tid":402344,"uid":25560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T11:09:34.000Z","msg":"要比$買kaspersky<br />\n<br />\n利申：用緊kaspersky"}]}